msContents.summary: Unattributed commentary on the summary of arithmetical operations by the late 13th- and early 14th-century scholar Ibn al-Bannāʼ. Demonstrates with examples the calculation of sums involving fractional numbers and square roots. Extensive marginal notes on a few leaves (p. 20-35). The first leaf is missing and several leaves have restored outer margins.

supportDesc.extent: 159 leaves : 268 x 195 (205 x 135) mm. bound to 274 x 208 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 159 leaves; [1-55, i-ii, 56-151, i-ii, 152-165, 164-273, 174-179, 280-312], later pagination in ink, upper center. Catchwords on each leaf, lower left verso, many obscured by past water damage.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in maghrebi script, with division headings written larger script.

origin.p: Written in northern Africa, probably Morocco, in the 15th century.

history.provenance: Sold by Sam Fogg Ltd. (London) to Lawrence J. Schoenberg, July 2004.
Deposit by Lawrence J. Schoenberg and Barbara Brizdle, 2013.
